{
  "texts": [
    "Patent information: All patents filed to the Japan Patent Office (Goto and Motohashi, 2017) at PATSTAT2020 Spring Version (those for which English-translated title and abstract information are available).",
    "Regarding the number of documents, we used 1,696,338 research papers and 12,330,725 patents, forming a total of 14,027,063 documents.",
    "Figure 1 shows the changes in the number of documents by publication year (for patents, the application year).",
    "The number of patents shows a declining trend since 2000, while the number of research papers remains stable, with ~ 100,000 publications per year.",
    "We followed two steps in creating document embedding vectors that represent the content of each document."
  ]
}